{"word":"ἐρινάζω","slug":"ἐρινάζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n42475\" key=\"e)rina/zw\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἐρῑν-άζω</orth>, <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> I <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρινάξαι</foreign> and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐρινάσαι,</foreign> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hsch.\">Hsch.</a></author> </bibl>:—<sense id=\"n42475.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">hang fruiting branches of the wild fig</tr_> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ἐρινεός</etym>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">near the cultivated fig</tr_> (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">συκῆ</etym>) in order that the gall-insect (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">ψήν</etym>) which lives in the wild fruit may carry pollen to the <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σῦκον,</foreign> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg002:2:9:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ CP\">CP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.9.5</biblScope> </bibl>:—<gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"voice\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pass.\">Pass.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὸ ἐρινασμένον</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the fig subjected to caprification,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg001:2:8:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HP\">HP</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.8.3</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n42475.1\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">gather wild figs,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0542.tlg001:7:143\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Poll.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.143</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}